    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, perfect for someone looking for a reliable car without the 'brand new' price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and it's ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
