    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and VANOS bulletproofing. The suspension geometry remains precise with upgraded poly-bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring the chassis handles with classic M-division neutrality. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
