    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example that perfectly balances performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel, consistent with responsible road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium seating shows only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all interior electronics\u2014including the navigation system and dual-zone climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is robust. It comes with a documented service history, having recently undergone a full multi-point inspection and synthetic oil service. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires offer substantial tread life for the seasons ahead. This is a turn-key vehicle that has been cared for with an eye for detail, offering the next owner a reliable and sophisticated driving experience.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
