    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in great shape for its next owner. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so while it has a little bit of character from regular use, it runs beautifully and feels super solid on the road. I\u2019ve really enjoyed driving it, and I\u2019m sure you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it or have any questions!",
      "price": 33500.0,
