    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power through a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with solid bushings and recent subframe reinforcement, ensuring the 50/50 weight distribution is fully exploited. While it displays honest cosmetic patina from spirited use, the powertrain delivers peak torque and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline without hesitation. A true driver\u2019s car with sorted internals and robust performance.",
